Fields:

[emph]Title[/emph]

Text: the title of the item, e.g.: 'How to choose a notebook'.
* Required field


[emph]Comment[/emph]

Textarea: some descriptive comment.
E.g.: 
1 - Compare quality and prices
2 - Test it
3 - Consult the team


[emph]Project[/emph]

Select: parent Project which contains the note, if none then select PHProjekt. 
* Required field


[emph]Tag[/emph]

The tag field that synchronizes the item with Tags panel.
